---
const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
---

<!-- Top marquee -->
<div class="marquee-bar" role="marquee" aria-label="CHOMPERZ announcements">
  <span class="marquee-track" aria-hidden="true">
    🦷 TEETH ARE SACRED &nbsp;✦&nbsp; FREE TOOTH READING WITH EVERY CLEANING &nbsp;✦&nbsp; NOW ACCEPTING BITCOIN, VIBES &amp; DENTAL INSURANCE (SPIRITUALLY) &nbsp;✦&nbsp; DR. MOLARSTONE HAS NEVER LOST A TOOTH* &nbsp;✦&nbsp; *THAT SHE WAS SUPPOSED TO KEEP &nbsp;✦&nbsp; OPEN 24/7 OR WHENEVER DR. MOLARSTONE WAKES UP &nbsp;✦&nbsp; MOUTH WHISPERING AVAILABLE TUESDAYS &nbsp;✦&nbsp; VOTED #1 DENTAL RAVE STUDIO IN THIS BUILDING &nbsp;✦&nbsp; 🦷 TEETH ARE SACRED &nbsp;✦&nbsp;
  </span>
</div>

<header>
  <a href="/" class="logo-wrap" aria-label="CHOMPERZ home">
    <span class="logo-main">CHOMPERZ™</span>
    <span class="logo-sub">Dental Experiences for the Spiritually Aligned</span>
  </a>
  <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
    <a href="/" class={currentPath === '/' ? 'nav-active' : ''}>Home</a>
    <a href="/schedule" class="nav-cta">Book Now 🦷</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<style>
header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 500;
  background: rgba(13,13,26,.96);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 3px solid #ff006e;
  box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,0,110,.4);
  padding: 14px 48px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
}

.logo-wrap {
  text-decoration: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}

.logo-main {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff006e, #00b4d8, #ccff00, #ff006e);
  background-size: 300% 100%;
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  animation: logoShimmer 3s linear infinite;
}

.logo-sub {
  font-size: .6rem;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

nav a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: .8rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 9px 18px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: all .2s;
}

nav a:hover,
nav a.nav-active {
  border-color: #ccff00;
  color: #ccff00;
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ccff00;
}

nav a.nav-cta {
  background: #ff006e;
  border-color: #ff006e;
  animation: navPulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

nav a.nav-cta:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
  background: #ff3399;
  color: #fff;
  box-shadow: none;
  border-color: #ff3399;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  header { padding: 14px 20px; }
  .logo-main { font-size: 1.5rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .logo-sub { display: none; }
  nav a:not(.nav-cta) { display: none; }
}
</style>
